NOTE:

This repository contains the code presented and used in the following paper, and it is no longer maintained:
http://www.geosci-model-dev.net/7/2831/2014/gmd-7-2831-2014.html

We have moved to the following repository:
https://github.com/geotopmodel/geotop/tree/se27xx


____________________________________________________________________

TO COMPILE: 

Type from this path:

mkdir bin # This is the directory for the executable file
make -f geotop.make

This will put the executable in the subdirectory "bin"
